r setting up equations. Since I can't do exact calculations here, I'll have to make reasonable adjustments based on the data provided and the given ranges. Finally, ensure all the adjusted quantities stay within practical cooking amounts and that the final recipe meets all the specified nutritional adjustments. Let me attempt to outline the steps and possible adjustments step by step considering each nutrient's requirements.":


